{"article_id":"OF2vwP2U6qh9oaBa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Donald Trump 's former attorney and fixer Michael Cohen testified in detail Wednesday about the President 's involvement in hush-money payments to women and his knowledge of longtime confidant Roger Stone 's efforts","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to contact WikiLeaks ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"while Trump 's Republican defenders aggressively worked to undermine Cohen 's credibility .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Cohen 's dramatic public testimony before the House Oversight Committee ping-ponged between Democrats","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"who walked Cohen through the actions","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Trump took","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and Republicans","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"who challenged Cohen over his financial crimes and past lies to Congress .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Cohen 's public testimony Wednesday was undoubtedly a spectacle ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"but its ultimate impact will depend upon whether Cohen 's allegations are viewed as credible .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Cohen 's hearing comes","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"while the President has his own big moment :","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Cohen is testifying about what he says are Trump 's misdeeds","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"while the President is in Vietnam","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"meeting with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Cohen also revealed","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that prosecutors in New York are investigating conversations between Trump and Cohen","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that occurred","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"after Cohen 's office was searched by the FBI in April 2018 .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"In his testimony , Cohen explained","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"how Trump instructed him to pay $ 130,000 to Stormy Daniels during the 2016 campaign for her silence about an alleged affair with Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"which Trump denies .","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"Trump then reimbursed Cohen as President for the payments ,","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"Cohen said","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"-","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"and he provided a copy of the check","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"to show it .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Cohen told the committee","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that there was `` no doubt in his mind ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that Trump knew","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"he was paying Cohen for `` hush money payments . ''","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"Further , Cohen testified","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump had called him in February 2018","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"to discuss messaging","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"surrounding the payment ,","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"where Trump directed him to lie about the President 's knowledge of the payment .","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"In his opening statement , Cohen launched a broadside against Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"accusing him of being `` a racist , '' `` a conman '' and `` a cheat . ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Cohen also talked about how Trump discussed the Trump Tower Moscow project with him into the 2016 campaign","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"- the topic","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"that Cohen would ultimately lie to Congress about -","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"and that Trump had knowledge of Stone 's efforts","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"to reach out to WikiLeaks ahead of the release of hacked Democratic emails during the 2016 campaign .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"`` The last time","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"I appeared before Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"I came to protect Mr. Trump .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Today I am here","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to tell the truth about Mr. Trump , ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Republicans pressed Cohen repeatedly on the crimes","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he pleaded guilty to ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"he had no credibility","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"having previously lied to Congress","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and that his own financial crimes","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"- which he pleaded guilty to","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"along with the campaign finance violations -","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"had nothing to do with Trump .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"Ohio Rep. Jim Jordan , the top Republican on the Oversight Committee , accused Cohen of turning against Trump","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"after he did not get a job at the White House .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"`` You wanted to work in the White House ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"you did n't get brought to the dance , ''","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"Jordan said .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"`` I was extremely proud to be the personal attorney for the President of the United States of America .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"I did not want to go to the White House , ''","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Cohen responded .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"But Republicans did n't buy Cohen 's answer ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"pointing to court filings from the Southern District of New York","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"that stated","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Cohen `` privately told friends and colleagues ,","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"including in seized text messages ,","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"that he expected to be given a prominent role and title in the new administration .","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"Cohen insisted","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"he did n't want a White House role ,","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"that prosecutors statement was `` not accurate . ''","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"Cohen , in fact , was angling for the White House chief of staff job ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"according to a person","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"who talked to him about it ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"and at one point there was a movement","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"to push him into the White House counsel 's office .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"The President suggested it to former White House counsel Don McGahn ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"but he said","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"Cohen did n't have the necessary experience and background","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"to work there ,","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"and Trump dropped it after that .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows , a North Carolina Republican , accused Cohen of lying in the hearing itself ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"pointing to documents","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he had filed with the committee","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"on whether he had any foreign contracts .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"he would review the form","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and amend it","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"if necessary .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"The White House said ahead of the hearing","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"it was `` laughable that anyone would take a convicted liar like Cohen at his word . ''","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Republicans hammered Cohen on the same theme ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"with one member calling Cohen","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"`` a pathological liar . ''","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Another Republican asked Cohen","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"what he would call himself","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"if he had called Trump a cheat .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Jordan and Cohen continued to battle throughout the hearing .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"After one exchange with another Republican , Jordan exclaimed :","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"`` His remorse is nonexistent ! ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"`` Shame on you , Mr. Jordan .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"That 's not what I said , ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Cohen shot back .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"When it was the Democrats ' turn","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"to question Cohen ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"they gave him the chance","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"to add new details","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"about how he had prepared his previous congressional testimony ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"in which he lied ,","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"as well as the hush money payments and Trump 's conversations with Stone .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Cohen also disclosed new information","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"when he said","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"he could not discuss conversations with Trump","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"that took place","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"two months","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"after the FBI raided his offices","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"because they were still under investigation .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"The Manhattan US Attorney 's Office ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"which prosecuted Cohen ,","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"is examining that conversation as well as other possible wrongdoing or illegal behavior by Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Cohen took his preparations for his 2017 congressional testimony into the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"telling one Democrat","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"that changes were made to his testimony about the Trump Tower Moscow project","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"when it was reviewed by Trump 's lawyers .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"`` There were several changes","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"that were made ,","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"including how we were going to handle that message , ''","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"`` The message , of course , being the length of time","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"that the Trump Tower Moscow project stayed ,","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"and remained alive . ''","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"Rep. Gerry Connolly , a Virginia Democrat , said","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"committee staff had uncovered an email","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"the White House had mistakenly released to lawmakers","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"that revealed a meeting","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"Trump had requested in May of 2017 with Cohen and Jay Sekulow , a member of the President 's legal team ,","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"where Cohen said","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"he discussed his upcoming testimony .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"Later , Cohen said","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"he did not know","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"who at the White House had edited his testimony ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"but that it had been circulated ,","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"including into the White House ,","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"because of a joint defense agreement .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Cohen also revealed","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"that he had discussed with Trump the public messaging","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"surrounding the payment to Daniels ,","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"that he had `` purposefully '' left Trump out of a statement last year to reporters","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"when he said","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"the campaign and Trump Organization were not involved with the payment .","depth":16},{"id":158,"text":"And Cohen discussed the details of a phone call","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"he said","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"that he had heard between Stone and Trump ,","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"in which Stone told Trump","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"that he had spoken by phone with Julian Assange","depth":16},{"id":163,"text":"and an email dump was coming","depth":17},{"id":164,"text":"that would hurt the Clinton campaign ,","depth":17},{"id":165,"text":"according to Cohen .","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"Cohen detailed several episodes","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"involving Trump ,","depth":16},{"id":168,"text":"from Trump arranging for the bidder of an auction for his portrait to when","depth":17},{"id":169,"text":"Cohen said","depth":17},{"id":170,"text":"he threatened Trump 's high school , his college and the College Board","depth":17},{"id":171,"text":"not to release his grades or test scores .","depth":17},{"id":172,"text":"Cohen also took a shot at Trump for his medical deferments during the Vietnam War ,","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"saying","depth":17},{"id":174,"text":"he asked Trump for medical records to about his bone spur","depth":19},{"id":175,"text":"to explain it to reporters ,","depth":19},{"id":176,"text":"but he was not provided any .","depth":18},{"id":177,"text":"`` I find it ironic , President Trump ,","depth":17},{"id":178,"text":"that you are in Vietnam right now , ''","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"Cohen provided new details","depth":16},{"id":181,"text":"claiming","depth":17},{"id":182,"text":"Trump was heavily involved in the pursuit of the Trump Tower Moscow project in 2016 .","depth":17},{"id":183,"text":"`` To be clear ,","depth":19},{"id":184,"text":"Mr. Trump knew of and directed the Trump Tower negotiations throughout the campaign","depth":20},{"id":185,"text":"and lied about it , ''","depth":20},{"id":186,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":18},{"id":187,"text":"`` He lied about it","depth":18},{"id":188,"text":"because he never expected to win the election .","depth":18},{"id":189,"text":"He also lied about it","depth":17},{"id":190,"text":"because he stood to make hundreds of millions of dollars on the Moscow real estate project . ''","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"CNN reported in July 2018","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"that Cohen was willing to testify to the special counsel","depth":16},{"id":193,"text":"that Trump knew in advance about the planned meeting at Trump Tower .","depth":16},{"id":194,"text":"Cohen said","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"that Trump did not `` directly '' tell him to lie to Congress ,","depth":15},{"id":196,"text":"but that Trump would tell him personally and the public","depth":17},{"id":197,"text":"that he had `` no business '' with Russia ,","depth":17},{"id":198,"text":"even as he was negotiating the Moscow project .","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"`` In his way , he was telling me to lie , ''","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"Republicans pushed back on the allegations .","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"Meadows brought to the hearing Lynne Patton , an African-American Department of Housing and Urban Development official","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"who worked with the Trump family before the campaign .","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"She stood behind him","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"and submitted a letter for the record ,","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"rebutting Cohen 's claims","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"about Trump being racist .","depth":16},{"id":208,"text":"Democrats argued","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"that Republicans were trying to sweep Cohen 's allegations under the table","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"to protect Trump .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"House Oversight Chairman Elijah Cummings , a Maryland Democrat , said","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"that the new evidence","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"Cohen provided","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"`` raises a host of troubling legal and ethical concerns about the President 's actions in the White House and before . ''","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"Jordan said","depth":12},{"id":216,"text":"that Cummings ' tenure would be marked","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"by bringing in Cohen ,","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"whom he labeled a `` fraudster , a cheat , convicted felon and , in two months , a federal inmate . ''","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":"Jordan responded","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"by charging","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"that Cummings ' tenure would be marked","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"by bringing in Cohen ,","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"whom he labeled a `` fraudster , a cheat , convicted felon and , in two months , a federal inmate . ''","depth":15},{"id":224,"text":"Wednesday 's hearing is the second of three congressional appearances for Cohen this week ,","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"after he appeared behind closed doors before the Senate Intelligence Committee on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"and will do the same before the House Intelligence Committee on Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"Cohen 's congressional appearances come","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"before he is scheduled to report to prison on May 6 for a three-year sentence","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"after he pleaded guilty to tax crimes , campaign finance violations and lying to Congress in 2017 .","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"Cummings said","depth":5},{"id":231,"text":"that he would not prevent committee members from asking questions about the Russia investigation at Wednesday 's hearing .","depth":5},{"id":232,"text":"Cummings had originally said","depth":7},{"id":233,"text":"the scope of the hearing would not include Russia ,","depth":7},{"id":234,"text":"but said at the hearing","depth":7},{"id":235,"text":"that after objections from Jordan , Russia questions were now within the scope of the hearing .","depth":7},{"id":236,"text":"Cummings said","depth":6},{"id":237,"text":"he was allowing the Russia questions also","depth":7},{"id":238,"text":"because Cohen made statements about the investigation in his written testimony ,","depth":8},{"id":239,"text":"and because they `` do not raise concern from the Department of Justice . ''","depth":8},{"id":240,"text":"This story has been updated with additional developments Wednesday","depth":2},{"id":241,"text":"and will continue to update throughout the day .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":483,"left":481,"right":482,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":481,"left":0,"right":480,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":480,"left":470,"right":479,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":470,"left":251,"right":469,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":249,"right":250,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":244,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":243,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":246,"right":247,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":246,"left":4,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":469,"left":326,"right":468,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":326,"left":259,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":255,"right":258,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":252,"right":254,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":13,"right":253,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":16,"right":257,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":257,"left":17,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":288,"right":324,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":282,"right":287,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":270,"right":281,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":270,"left":266,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":261,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":20,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":263,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":262,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":28,"right":268,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":29,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":281,"left":276,"right":280,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":274,"right":275,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":32,"right":273,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":33,"right":272,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":271,"right":36,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":37,"right":38,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":278,"right":279,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":39,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":49,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":284,"right":285,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":46,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":296,"right":323,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":289,"right":295,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":52,"right":294,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":290,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":292,"right":58,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":291,"right":57,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":303,"right":322,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":300,"right":302,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":297,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":298,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":302,"left":301,"right":66,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":322,"left":312,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":67,"right":311,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":307,"right":310,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":307,"left":68,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":69,"right":305,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":72,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":308,"right":309